    This class is used to store data on the floor map for a base map.

    This class is used to store data on the floor's layer, which is the type or classification of the various POIs that can be shown.

    The MapConfig class represents the configuration for the maps used in the application.

    This class is used to store data on the Point of Interest.

    This class is used to store the user's configuration data, such as their username and password
    UserData
    Represents user-specific data, such as user-created layers and favorite Points of Interest (POIs).
    UserLayer
    This class is used to store data on the user layer which is just a bit of extra data for a layer but specifically for the user
    UserList
    This class is used to store the list of users, the list contains the user's configuration (username and password)
